      <title>塞浦路斯总统接受联合国邀请就数十年争端进行会谈</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/what-is-the-cyprus-problem-and-is-there-hope-for-a-solution</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞浦路斯总统尼科斯·赫里斯托杜利迪斯接受联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯的邀请，出席与土耳其塞浦路斯领导人埃尔辛·塔塔尔的三方会谈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/what-is-the-cyprus-problem-and-is-there-hope-for-a-solution</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 04 Aug 2024 07:31:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾与德国同意完成广泛防御安排</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-04/philippines-germany-agree-to-complete-broad-defense-arrangement</link>
      <description><![CDATA[德国和菲律宾表示，双方同意推动达成广泛的防务合作安排。]]></description>
